profile:
Providing quality paint and sundry products to the Greater Area Halifax for over 20 years.  Expert service, custom colour matching.  Custom window treatments, full service Hunter Douglas gallery.  

Our product line includes Hunter Douglas blinds, shutters, silhouette shadings, Duette honeycomb blinds. Dulux and Glidden paint and related products.

profile:
Welcome to Budget Blinds of Halifax and Dartmouth. We're your local experts and are proud to be backed by the #1 provider of custom window coverings in North America that has provided design-driven solutions for over 25 years. With the highest levels of customer satisfaction, you'll have the peace of mind and security that comes with choosing the proven leader. We’ll get to know you and your unique style so we can deliver the perfect solution for your home. 

***

Explore what Beautiful can do for your windows. Contact us today to schedule your appointment. We’re looking forward to working with you.
